title: Classic Leather Credit Card Holder
description: The Rich Roots Classic Leather Credit Card Holder is crafted entirely in 100% Calfskin, and accented with the Rich Roots pomegranate logo in metallic silver. The card holder features a center slip with 2 card slots on each side, allowing to hold up to 5 credit cards.

title: Organizer 2.0
description: The Organizer 2.0 Briefcase is perfect for your laptop, files, and tablets. Given enough room for a slim finish. Ideal for the freelancers and pros.

title: Black Saffiano Micro Pouch
description: The Micro Pouch is perfect for anyone with an “on-the-go” lifestyle. The wristlet can hold your phone, card holders, and a few of your other favorite essentials.

title: Metallic Saffiano Micro Bag
description: The Micro’s contemporary design and organized interior makes this handbag your go-to everyday bag. It can be draped on the shoulder, worn cross-body, or even carried by hand by doubling the leather handles with its chain.

title: Hard Rich
description: Inspired by the look and feel of raw gold, the Hard Rich ring represents the weight of development - with all its depth and dimension. Open and rough edged but bridged by its foundation. Dipped in 18k gold, brushed with an antique finish.

title: Mihr
description: Named after the Armenian God of Sun and deity of Heaven Light , the Mihr Ring represents the obscurity in between. Dipped in 18k gold, brushed with an antique finish.
